{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21141.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"空穂 夏希","nameRight":"牧 カオル","textRight":"…で、気が付いたらかずみと海香@がいなくなっていて…","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301}],"textRight":"この公園にいたんだ@あたしひとりでね"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"そんなことが…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300201}],"textLeft":"それってやっぱり@魔女の仕業…だよね…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":1}],"textRight":"根拠はないけど@それ以外に説明はつかないよね"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"…なんというか、ずいぶん@落ち着いているというか…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":100}],"textRight":"…普段から色々起きてるからね@これくらいなら大丈夫"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301}],"textRight":"あと、あたしサッカーやってて@それで、鍛えてるから…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":1}],"textRight":"メンタルもフィジカルもね！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":300}],"textRight":"…とかいいつつチャンスに@シュート、外したりするけどね…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301}],"textRight":"はははは…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"カオルさんみたいな子と@仲間だったら心強いだろうな…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":100}],"textRight":"じゃあ、仲間になろ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:300201:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]え!?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"頼らせてもらえると@ありがたいんだけど…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300201}],"textLeft":"…え…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"…じゃあ、私でよければ…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300201}],"textLeft":"よろしくお願いします@カオルさん！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":100}],"textRight":"カオルでいいよ！@よろしくね！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"早速なんだけどさ…神浜のことを@教えてもらいたいんだ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401301}],"textRight":"どこに人が多く集まっているとか@逆にここは人が少ないとか…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":400}],"textRight":"…あ、そうだ…そもそも、ここ…@この公園がどこなのか…とかも！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300201,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"…任せて、カオル！"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_03"}],"nameCenter":"牧 カオル","textCenter":"神浜の魔法少女…一体、@どんな子なんだろう…？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401301,"motion":300}]},{"chara":[{"id":401301}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}